  "original_title": "\u0db6\u0dd2\u0dad\u0dca\u0dad\u0dbb - \u0d9a\u0dd4\u0d9a\u0dd4\u0dbd\u0dca \u0db8\u0dc3\u0dca \u0db8\u0dd2\u0dbd \u0d85\u0da9\u0dd4 \u0d9a\u0dbb\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1 \u0dc3\u0dcf\u0d9a\u0da0\u0dca\u0da1\u0dcf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Negotiations to reduce egg-chicken prices",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Director General of Consumer Affairs Authority S. said that the main producers of eggs and chicken expressed their willingness to reduce the prices of eggs and they requested to provide solutions to several problems of the producers in order to reduce the prices. T. Mr. Kodikara said today (17).",
        "Mr. Kodikara said that the producers of eggs and chicken meat clarified the facts about the increase in their production costs and also mentioned that the consumer authority worked to inform about the market information of the two food items.",
        "Mr. Kodikara further said that he is confident that the issues regarding the price of eggs and chicken can be resolved.",
        "After the discussions held today (17) at the consumer authority with the representatives of the two main associations of egg and chicken meat producers, the director general of that authority S. T. Mr. Kodikara said so."
      ],
